  "detailed_description": "<h1>❤ COMING SOON Q1 2022 ❤</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Drag your card to interact with the environment cards to complete each level.<br></li><li>Collectible Item - along all the stage, player will have chances to retrieve items from character and understand more about them.<br></li><li>Many different RPG card types to make various unique choice decisions. <br></li><li>Many kawaii girls from different designs are waiting for you!!<br></li><li>Various interactions follow up with the character.<br></li><li>Cute voice with different personalities from every character.<br></li><li>Gallery and character viewer features.<br></li><li>Good luck and happy ending!!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426110/extras/936d2d59e2c57af41782eb259f7d806c.poster.avif?t=1673411034\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426110/extras/936d2d59e2c57af41782eb259f7d806c.webm?t=1673411034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
